.e from search to confirm to track to rating. These APIs don\u2019t necessarily need to be called in order every time. There are use cases where one may call the confirm API directly without going through the search, select and init."), mdx("h3", null, "Support APIs"), mdx("p", null, mdx("span", _extends({
